race.comment: WITHOUT A TRACE (5) hit the ground running last start and was never headed (41.37) at Wentworth Park in NG over 720m. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. In top form and looks a key chance again. ETHANOL WATER (8) continues to race in super honest form, hitting the frame three times on end before scoring an overdue win last time out (41.81) at Sandown. Form at this distance is sound. Will go close here with a clear run. PASS MARK (2) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 7 last time (42.61) at Sandown. The form from his last run stacks up well. Expected to feature. LATE NIGHT NEWS (7) has a solid strike rate at this distance.
